    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think it''s less focused on the coal side of things and my value is more aligned with that. They''re much more people focused, I think.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Friends to me in Orange Sky are the people I work with. They''re the people who access our services. Everyone''s the same when you come here.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I''ll be working within the next, I don''t know, a year or two. I think I''ll be working in the next, by Christmas.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW());
INSERT INTO airtable_quotes (id, quote_text, context, theme, created_at)
VALUES 
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'This is not detention, it''s actually about a developmental environment and it''s about working with kids and their families.', NULL, 'Comfort', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I was just so impressed with the process and the professionalism of it all. It''s just amazing.', NULL, 'Innovation', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'They''ve always been nice, always been good, yeah.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I like go back to my own homeland and teach my kids all them things, what I done, you know, instead of wanting them to drink here, I want them to go back to where my homeland, ''cause my homeland is no alcoholic, no drugs at all.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'There''s hope for everyone. Even for this guy down there with the slingy.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'It encourages people to stay together and to be able to get through tough times.', NULL, 'Long-term Health Outcomes', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'If you know where you come from, people can''t say why don''t you get back to where you come from? If they can''t hunt us away from here, you''re walking around our country, you are the guest. That''s the safeness in that culture.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think it''s a conversation. Look, we, we have people who come here and just sit down and have a chat without doing any washing.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I just want to have a room, bedroom, because I don''t even have a bedroom. And yeah, peace.', NULL, 'Comfort', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think toughness could be out there for a lot of people in general.', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Just from my observations probably is that the further the community people live out from the main central area, I can see it being harder.', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'It just feels good to volunteer... I find this is very similar.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Listening is a really important skill to have... it''s equally as important to learn when to just sit back and listen and observe.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'You can hang out, you can have a chat. Also here at the neighborhood center, same thing.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'It''s a matter of sustainability in the end. The ability to wash clothes ensures that resources are not spent on buying new items all the time.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I grew up in a washing machine where you just push that $1 in, you know, and, and that, that, that machine, when we used to use it, we used to wash, there was like 15 people living in the house where were all young fellas, right up to old people.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'This is really special for me. I grew, my career started here on Palm Island. So I began teaching straight out of uni here. So I''ve known some of these people in the team for quite a number of years and to circle back here in a different space has been absolutely incredible.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think I use the terminology fair and firm. Fair talks about all those ands, love respect, kindness, empathy, understanding, and trying to really lean on that fair.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'We''ve made it work... Just work. We''ve made it work.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think there are a lot of times that people on shift, especially at night encounter people who are using drugs or are on drugs at the time that they come to shift.', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Our service providers bring the food, which is good for people''s sustenance. But it''s that time in between when people get the chance to talk.', NULL, 'Comfort', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I go out to Boulder Camp and Ningamai every day, supporting them with breakfast, cold water, hot cups of tea, coffee.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'They should have a back up person or train someone up.', NULL, 'Innovation', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I''m not interested in drugs.', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'For the homeless people, I think it''s as tough as anywhere in the world... If you''ve got nowhere to sleep and not much to eat, doesn''t matter where you are, does it?', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'To be clean and have clean clothes. If you''ve got that all the time you take it for granted but for someone who hasn''t got any of it to come here and be able to be clean, have clean clothes, change the clothes, it''s powerful as a human being to have dignity in that.', NULL, 'Comfort', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'If you don''t provide services and activities for young people, then you''re almost encouraging them to go and find their own opportunities for entertainment or thrill-seeking.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I just encourage them the best you can and just be there, supportive and all that. Family''s there for support, but it''s always good to have that extra support on the side for it.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I didn''t wanna think I was basically homeless, say bum on the street and stuff like that, yeah.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'We''re actively working towards hopefully filling a gap in that space as well.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Why is a good night''s sleep? Good.', NULL, 'Long-term Health Outcomes', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'People need purpose. People need a place to call home. People need a place where they see themselves within a bigger story.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'He says that it is very important that what I told you before, John, is that you have to know that there is no educator there, they are all security and none of them trust security and security don''t trust the kids.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Our Elders are a really key source of knowledge. We shouldn’t just think that science on its own is the best way to understand the world. Elders provide another source of knowledge, another way of understanding the world, and bringing that together is so important.', NULL, 'Youth Engagement', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I''ve always had a strong sense of justice in my life, not necessarily as a child, defining it as justice, but when I reflect back on my childhood, I always had this sense of things needing to be just and fair and equal for people.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I can see that just having conversations with people and providing that service for people, it''s helping them out.', NULL, 'Long-term Health Outcomes', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'We put together like, went to like a, tied up with a little plastic, like a crate.', NULL, 'Innovation', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I have changed a lot here. The change, right? I have changed a lot.', NULL, 'Personal Growth', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think the social interaction is very important. It is giving me a safe space in the community to talk about my life and the things I''m wanting to do.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'The majority of children who are in the center have no crime, but they basically have no family. So they put them in prison?', NULL, 'Long-term Health Outcomes', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'You need to have a home that you can call home and that you''re happy with, and the wind can flow in and out and you can have your family there.', NULL, 'Comfort', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think they really did their homework in placing it here. The free bus from the city comes right across the road, so that''s fantastic.', NULL, 'Innovation', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'A lot of them call me a pop or grandpa, you know, because they haven''t got that connection with any families. A lot of them are in care and that''s what they need.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'There''s a cohort of people out there who don''t access our services. Whether they don''t know how to or they don''t have the confidence to. And I think that''s still really sad.', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Tenant Creek is a small community town, which has different language groups here. Everyone knows everyone.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'It''s not just donating to a charity. It''s getting down here. It''s cooking the snags yourself and it''s giving to these people.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'It''s being at the coalface, actually seeing and seeing the impact you''re actually having a part of, as opposed to, you know, handing over some money and a cheque and, and not quite knowing what that''s going to do or what they''re going to do with that.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think there''s a lot more growth to happen, particularly in the Serena community. I think there''s a lot more that can do.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'It just seems to me that should be a priority for government to get people off the streets and into shelter.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Not one of our members has committed suicide...I trust that what you saw today...was pretty straightforward and upfront.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW());
