    (gen_random_uuid(), 'A bit of it''s like service, but then a bit of it''s like connection and conversation.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'A lot of the people, they come here for a meal. They might come here for meals, they''ll get their washing done, they go somewhere else tomorrow night for a meal.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think this is an amazing opportunity to be able to support people with their hygiene needs, which is a basic necessity in a global scale.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Hopefully they''re going to put orange sky, the sleep bus down near the park, near the police station.', NULL, 'Innovation', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'We''ve gotta create a custodian economy that isn''t reliant on funding or a policy to make the change.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'We should be entitled to do what we''ve got to do with it, any way we have to.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I''ve been homeless for first of about a month. Before that I was in temporary accommodation where there was limited, limited services.', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Volunteering is part of life, but it''s getting less and less because people need money... People need to be paid for their work.', NULL, 'Innovation', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I reckon it''ll last a long time, yeah.', NULL, 'Long-term Health Outcomes', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I stumbled across Orange Sky in the news in the Newcastle Herald quite some years ago. And I thought, hmm, this might suit me.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'So we''re going, we''ve been at Kalgoorlie, Tennant, Mount Isa and stuff. What do you reckon we need to do to make sure these beds work in community for those places?', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Everyone''s generally respectful and everyone has their bad days, but for the most part, we try to help each other out and get through this.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think the main thing I love is our friends and the people I volunteer with. It''s a really lovely atmosphere. I think it''s a very community-heavy atmosphere and yeah, they keep me coming back.', NULL, 'Human Connection', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Homelessness is not just about people living on the street. But also homelessness is people that live in inadequate houses, in houses without water, without electricity.', NULL, 'Harsh Living Conditions', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I grew up in a language I never spoke English in, in, in the kindergarten school when me and my older sister started off going to school in that kindergarten school, they used to come and talk in language before we spoke English and tell us what to say.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'We can''t just address those two components of justice without addressing all aspects of justice entirely.', NULL, 'Community Support', NOW()),
    (gen_random_uuid(), 'I think the Orange Sky, however it is put into community, will flourish.', NULL, 'Sustainability', NOW()),
